<p>Dude, you&#8217;re a writer. Of code, of prose. You&#8217;ve got it; now, it&#8217;s up to you to choose what to work at and make stronger.</p>

<p>I&#8217;d advise that you avoid kicking yourself for working on whichever of the two you choose to work on, on any given day.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.gibberish.com">misuba</a>
